You have to copy the following jars from you spectrum installation ($SPEC_ROOT/SDK/lib/)
or add them to the build path.  This list is not tuned, some of the jars might not be needed.

clientapp.jar
ems90.jar
global90.jar
jsafeJCEFIPS.jar
lm.jar
mindterm.jar
modelinggateway90.jar
mte.jar
ncm90.jar
omi90.jar
processd.jar
productsuite90.jar
sanct6.jar
sanctuary.jar
sbgwimport90.jar
snmpsrv90.jar
ssorb90.jar
ssorbutil90.jar
util90.jar
utilapp90.jar
utilgui90.jar
utilnet90.jar
utilsrv90.jar
vbhelper90.jar
vbjorb.jar
vbsec.jar
